text: McKinley Park may refer to a place in the United States: * McKinley Park, Alaska, a census-designated place in the Denali Borough * McKinley Park, Chicago, Illinois, a neighborhood * McKinley Park, Sacramento, California, a neighborhood park ==See also== * Denali National Park and Preserve, known as Mount McKinley National Park from 1917 to 1980
title: McKinley Park
